nodes.text: Keelyvine Reus's Delta-7B Aethersprite-class light interceptor
Keelyvine Reus flew a Delta-7B Aethersprite-class light interceptor during the Clone Wars.

Jedi Master Keelyvine Reus flew this green marked Delta-7B starfighter with her R4 unit during the battle of Ukio. She, her Padawan Tyzen Xebec and Kit Fisto inspected the Ukian planetary shield and its main shield generator, when Ukio was attacked by Separatists. Fisto and Reus went to their Jedi fighters to do a quick recon in the area the Separatist ship was seen. They saw a Lucrehulk-class battleship launching dozens of modified seismic tanks into the atmosphere of Ukio.
